{"tid":930034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【下籤】何志平同志03年車公廟所求嘅第83籤","createTime":"2018-12-06T04:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T09:27:58.000Z","uid":54337,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e0b7ea8f665acf74967d82dd53bb9c5ecf9ef2","tid":930034,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"第八十三籤下籤<br />\n<br />\n籤文：<br />\n掛帆順水上楊州，<br />\n半途頗耐浪打頭；<br />\n實力撐持難寸進，<br />\n落橈下𢃇水難流。<br />\n<br />\n解曰「凡事不吉」。"},{"pid":"3f78a2bf326ff58b9ece7c0a2a1e4174e7e818a4","tid":930034,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:23:13.000Z","msg":"車公好靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8476ca72b93817ab0600134d0149e2ab877ead7","tid":930034,"uid":131064,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:24:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回力籤</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d37e79e05ed6e7a5a87fcf7cd7810f38f457332","tid":930034,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"掛帆順水上楊州<br />\n<br />\n成句根本係形容何同志後生時候，精英，讀音樂，讀化學物理，之後讀醫，哈佛讀書，中大教書，做埋眼科名醫，順風順水。"},{"pid":"8003cd55db868a897ea0f7b3d1bcb109a26136bc","tid":930034,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d37e79e05ed6e7a5a87fcf7cd7810f38f457332","tid":930034,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"掛帆順水上楊州<br />\n<br />\n成句根本係形容何同志後生時候，精英，讀音樂，讀化學物理，之後讀醫，哈佛讀書，中大教書，做埋眼科名醫，順風順水。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e355662864531e7352cea0e37f9d1e98f298b54","tid":930034,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:50:19.000Z","m